{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ef70ce53bb","title":"对林彪在接见全国各地来京师生大会上的讲话稿的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bf010dcc28","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":31,"articleId":"ef70ce53bb"}],"tags":[{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"63287a3723","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ef70ce53bb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林彪，在中共八届十一中全会上继续当选为中央政治局常委，不久被称中央副主席。"},{"id":"3d6c90ca73","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ef70ce53bb","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"年8月31日下午，毛泽东和中共中央其他领导人一起在天安门广场接见了来自北京及全国各地的五十万师生和红卫兵。林彪和周思来分别发表讲话。本篇是毛泽东对林彪8月31日送审的讲话稿的批语。"},{"id":"006bf2589f","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ef70ce53bb","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指林彪在送审的讲话稿中加写的两句话，即在讲话稿中“革命的小将们，毛主席和党中央热烈赞扬你们敢想，敢说，敢干，敢问，敢革命的无产阶级革命精神。你们千了大量的好事，你们提出了大量的好倡议。我们十分高兴，我们热烈支持你们”这段话后面，加写了“坚决反对压制你们！你们的革命行动好得很！”"}],"contents":[{"id":"1feaeb5162","type":"title","text":"对林彪在接见全国各地来京师牛大会上的讲话稿的批语2","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ef70ce53bb"},{"id":"63287a3723","type":"paragraph","text":"退林彪同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ef70ce53bb"},{"id":"3d6c90ca73","type":"paragraph","text":"这样修改很好。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ef70ce53bb"},{"id":"006bf2589f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ef70ce53bb"},{"id":"fc55f5f51a","type":"paragraph","text":"八月开一日上午十一时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ef70ce53bb"}],"page":{"id":"a860cd5b2b","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ef70ce53bb","start":29,"end":29}}}},"__N_SSG":true}